text:
nei yih doo khat leh kriing chni maang;
noom suul k'er tun mhei prngat chda; dii kluung ser-ser thuh mhei txhii chda;
mma ngi ruu tang ren mpii chda; mma' miing lei yih rin kndit lam thah mtxhii chda;
kdi you arlim ki daam yool thuh nei yih chet daat yo ring, nei yih ktxhaa kma' avah txii chmaang; mlei a Nang ngi ado ttxhii chaak; Nah akchung le' akuikin nih ado tdao pik;
nei mhei kpteng rek maai txhuum mih kmaal rang ki mhei prchuul pik chti nu; tkyat krvei mal paa khat hep pih mkool chti nu, nei a kdo kriin doo khat leh am meh.
nei krin khuu mkheng thuh ktxhaa le' von sat ava ngi mhei ktxhii chrah; ung ngu ktxuu knaai kma' mkpuu Nah inn thuh am chnik di'.
